channel.title: RSCFastlay!
channel.description:
Well okey, I'm hosting a RSC server , it has all skills besides Agility . Stable encomy... new server so need miners and smithers ;) server has a decent xp , ( low about 7-9x from real rsc ) .. there is one problem with client - client needs apache, no problem got it with client only thing you need to do is copy paste apache-ant1.7.0 from the folder to C:\ disk and you can run the client No registration, just choose your name and password and logg in. Server is 24/7 up and down only when has services or some problems
-fully working mining, smithing, fleching, woodcut, firemaking, crafting, all combat skills, magic, herblore, prayer, ranged, fishing, cooking and theaving. all skills work expect agility
Links are in Sig. TnX
